videos.headline: Iowa WR comes up with a smooth one-handed grab
videos.description: Iowa WR Ihmir Smith-Marsette races down the field and comes up with an outstanding one-handed catch and dances down the sidelines.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Iowa WR comes up with a smooth one-handed grab) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa defender punches the ball out in red zone
videos.description: Purdue WR Amad Anderson Jr. can't hold on to the ball as he gets hit, and Iowa's Matt Hankins comes up with the fumble.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Iowa defender punches the ball out in red zone) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's Bell makes diving TD catch
videos.description: Purdue's David Bell jukes his defender and makes an incredible diving catch for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Purdue's Bell makes diving TD catch) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa's Moss picks off Plummer
videos.description: Purdues QB Jack Plummer tries to press a pass between two defenders, but Riley Moss climbs the ladder for the Iowa interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-play (Iowa's Moss picks off Plummer) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa's Goodson leaps into end zone for first career TD
